# ElevenLabs TTS / Voice
# ⚠️  ROTATE REQUIRED: The previous ElevenLabs key was committed to Git history and is compromised.
# 1. Go to https://elevenlabs.io → Profile → API Keys → delete the old key → create a new one.
# 2. Replace PASTE_YOUR_NEW_ELEVENLABS_KEY_HERE below with the new key.
# 3. Set the same key in your Vercel project environment variables (for apps/landing and web-revamp).
# 4. Never commit this file with a real key value.
ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=PASTE_YOUR_NEW_ELEVENLABS_KEY_HERE

# Site URL (used for OAuth/callbacks if needed)
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://casa-landing.vercel.app
